 that KK Higgs\nbosons are generally an indispensable part of the warped 5D SM, and their\nphenomenology such as signals at the LHC are worth further investigation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 19 Dec 2014 18:07:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-22"}
